पिपरगाँव गाँव, फर्रुखाबाद (फर्रुखाबाद)

पिपरगाँव फर्रुखाबाद, फर्रुखाबाद, उत्तर प्रदेश स्थित एक गाँव है।

For Pipergaon You can catch train or bus. You can also use ur own vehicle.

Hanuman Mandir, Gov. Hospital,Shri krishan madir, shiv mandir, Devi mandir and Sarvoday inter college are famous place of Pipergaon.
Every navrate in chaitra a fair use to held there. A welknown singer Mohanendra Pratap Singh(MohanMonu) S/O Thakur Ashok Kumar Singh(MOTA WALE) is born in Pipergaon In khinni mohalla.He participate in SAREGAMAPA Singing Superstar In 2012.
